{"tid":643431,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳綺莉女兒卓林加拿大街頭現身 嚷：我想找我爸","createTime":"2018-04-26T13:14:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T13:17:31.000Z","uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9c23e6177f1ef34a71f04c326df178c1de1225","tid":643431,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:14:35.000Z","msg":"藝人吳綺莉被指與女兒吳卓林失去聯絡，據悉卓林辭工失蹤數月，吳綺莉曾報警求助，警方列作失蹤人口案處理，而吳綺莉在接受訪問時表示知道個女不在港，在朋友家中居住。 <br />\n<br />\n不過，卓林終於現身了！今日網上有條片，片中見卓林身在加拿大與同學在超巿中，而與她一起的還有她的網紅女友Andi，卓林於片中有點迷惘說：「我想找我爸&hellip;&hellip;我媽&hellip;&hellip;我知道&hellip;&hellip;但是我媽&hellip;&hellip;」 <br />\n<br />\n今次卓林飛到外地「尋爸」，不少網民都直呼「可憐！」更有人指卓林淪落街頭，還叫朋友收留她。"},{"pid":"cd6316425344884e4a563302071d4d02ee470ba5","tid":643431,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180426/photo/bkn-20180426162551838-0426_00862_001_02p.jpg?20180426171508\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180426162551838-0426_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20180426171508&h=eee6dda1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180426/photo/bkn-20180426162551838-0426_00862_001_04p.jpg?20180426171508\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180426%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180426162551838-0426_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20180426171508&h=5edb8ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n短片清楚看到卓林用普通話說：「我想找我爸&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n卓林（左）與網紅女友Andi一同現身超市。"},{"pid":"e5997592c5133a97ccdef46b494a360d7e41c378","tid":643431,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"搵老豆梗係去人大會堂門口<br />\n去加拿大批柒"}]}